{
  "stem": "24111.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all the Americans and British soldiers, which were in the military prisoner of war camp, escaped in the countryside.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they tried to make their way either south to the, to the frontier, where the fighting was, and cross over to their troop, to their side.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or they tried to do the same thing what we did, go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some of the older boys joined this group and went south.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a few managed to cross the German lines into the British lines and American lines and actually made it to Palestine in 1942 when the war was going on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "A lot of those prisoners, I told you, where they camp was opened up, made it through and we went to the alliance.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I have to mention one boy, because he should get recognition, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "His name is Max Federman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And Max Federman was my age.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was a native of Frankfurt, Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And Max Federman went down south to reach the British-American forces, but didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He made it to the partisans in the Apennine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he was one of the most recognized partisan fighter in the Italian war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he got-- after the war-- medals from the Italian government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the American government recognized him and gave him a preferred quota to emigrate in 1945 to the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I want to recognize Max Federman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He lives in California today, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But again, to come back to our situation, we knew we had to escape to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Joschko sent Pacifici Chichibo to Milano, and from there, to Como Chiasso to the Swiss border, to find out the possibility of an escape route to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
